### `provisionKey`

**Signature:** `fleetEnabled validRequest vaultResult keyIsActive`

//////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////
4. Decision logic
//////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////
4.1 [provisionKey](#provisionkey)

| # | Condition | Result |
|---|-----------|--------|
| 1 | ~ fleetEnabled | [PR_Disabled](#provisionresult) |
| 2 | ~ validRequest | [PR_BadRequest](#provisionresult) |
| 3 | vaultResult != [KV_Ok](#keyvaultresult) | [PR_InternalError](#provisionresult) |
| 4 | keyIsActive | [PR_Unauthorized](#provisionresult) |
| 5 | *(otherwise)* | [PR_Succeeded](#provisionresult) |

#### Related Properties
- [P2 — Active Prevents Provisioning](#p2--active-prevents-provisioning)
- [P5 — Disabled Rejects All](#p5--disabled-rejects-all)
- [P15 — Can Provision When Ready](#p15--can-provision-when-ready)
- [P20 — Bad Request Distinct](#p20--bad-request-distinct)

<details><summary>Formal definition (Cryptol)</summary>

```cryptol
provisionKey fleetEnabled validRequest vaultResult keyIsActive =
  if ~ fleetEnabled        then PR_Disabled
   | ~ validRequest        then PR_BadRequest
   | vaultResult != KV_Ok  then PR_InternalError
   | keyIsActive           then PR_Unauthorized
  else                          PR_Succeeded
```

</details>

### `enrollDevice`

**Signature:** `fleetEnabled validMetadata authResult activationResult`

4.2 [enrollDevice](#enrolldevice) (activate)

| # | Condition | Result |
|---|-----------|--------|
| 1 | ~ fleetEnabled | [ER_Disabled](#enrollmentresult) |
| 2 | ~ validMetadata | [ER_Unauthorized](#enrollmentresult) |
| 3 | authResult == [AR_Authenticated](#authresult) |  |
| 4 | activationResult == [AC_Success](#activationresult) | [ER_Succeeded](#enrollmentresult) |
| 5 | activationResult == [AC_AlreadyActive](#activationresult) | [ER_Unauthorized](#enrollmentresult) |
| 6 | *(otherwise)* | [ER_InternalError](#enrollmentresult)) |
| 7 | authResult == [AR_VaultUnavailable](#authresult) | [ER_InternalError](#enrollmentresult) |
| 8 | *(otherwise)* | [ER_Unauthorized](#enrollmentresult) |

#### Related Properties
- [P1 — Key Monotonicity](#p1--key-monotonicity)
- [P5 — Disabled Rejects All](#p5--disabled-rejects-all)
- [P10 — Missing Metadata Fails](#p10--missing-metadata-fails)
- [P16 — Authenticated Activation Succeeds](#p16--authenticated-activation-succeeds)
- [P19 — Vault Unavailable Is Internal](#p19--vault-unavailable-is-internal)
- [P21 — Activate Without Metadata Unauthorized](#p21--activate-without-metadata-unauthorized)
- [P22 — Activation Io Failure Is Internal](#p22--activation-io-failure-is-internal)

<details><summary>Formal definition (Cryptol)</summary>

```cryptol
enrollDevice fleetEnabled validMetadata authResult activationResult =
  if ~ fleetEnabled                       then ER_Disabled
   | ~ validMetadata                      then ER_Unauthorized
   | authResult == AR_Authenticated       then
        (if activationResult == AC_Success       then ER_Succeeded
          | activationResult == AC_AlreadyActive then ER_Unauthorized
         else                                         ER_InternalError)
   | authResult == AR_VaultUnavailable    then ER_InternalError
  else                                         ER_Unauthorized
```

</details>

